title.rendered: STEDI ST3301 PRO 27.5 Inch 18 LED Light Bar

content.rendered:
STEDI ST3301 PRO 27.5 Inch 18 LED Light Bar

BUILT TO SHINE.

Advancing from our popular ST3301 comes the new STEDI ST3301 Pro. With a new look and improved lighting technology, in addition to our revised reflectors, the ST3301 Pro will increase your lighting performance dramatically.

SUPERIOR DESIGN. EXEMPLARY INNOVATION.

Our ST3301 Pro builds from the character of the ST3K and ST4K, by offering a higher Lumen output with an excellent mid-range volume. The ST3301 packs a greater punch than its predecessor when it comes to light penetration, offering a light reach of up to 600m at the 1 Lux mark. With this increase of light, we also managed to maintain a streamlined design, keeping the weight of the 27.5″ Bar at 2.80kg.

COLOURS OF EXPRESSION.

Add your own personal colour combination with our customisable side caps. Grey and STEDI orange caps are included, and when you get sick of those, indulge yourselves with the green, blue, and red caps which are available to purchase separately.
